title: Bobby’s Fiancé Thinks There’s A Ghost At The House + Dierks Bentley Brings Us His New Music + Raymundo Is Dealing With Wedding Drama
itunes:title: Bobby’s Fiancé Thinks There’s A Ghost At The House + Dierks Bentley Brings Us His New Music + Raymundo Is Dealing With Wedding Drama
description:
Bobby calls his fiancé Caitlin after she heard a strange noise coming from their bedroom. Could it possible a spirit that Lunchbox brought back with him from the Murder House? Our friend, Dierks Bentley stops by to talk new music, life in Colorado and his top career songs. Raymundo shares his Top 5 wedding dramas going into this weekend.
